  <longdescription>
    Implementation of <a href="http://www.robotfrontier.com/papers/cira97.pdf">frontier exploration</a> for ROS, extending on the existing navigation stack (costmap_2d, move_base).
  It accepts exploration goals via <a href="http://www.ros.org/wiki/actionlib">actionlib</a> (Rviz UI provided), sends movement commands to <a href="http://www.ros.org/wiki/move_base">move_base</a>.
